<div class="main-section" style="text-align:center">
    <h1 style=" font-size: 20px;">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <div style="text-align:left">
        <p><p>TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</p>

        <ol>
            <li>The &ldquo;TOYOTA YARIS Photo contest&ldquo; is organized by Toyota Kirloskar Motor Private Limited (The organizer)</li>
            <li>To be eligible for the participation, Participant must be an Indian resident who has completed the age of 18 years at the time of participation in the contest.</li>
            <li>The &ldquo;TOYOTA YARIS Photo contest&ldquo; shall be open from 00:00 hours on Saturday, (DD/MM/YYYY), and closes on Sunday (DD/MM/YYYY) at 23:59 hours. All participants must participate in the Digital contest at the Mall activity to qualify.</li>
            <li>The participation in the contest is purely voluntary. The contest process is defined as follows: Fill the database form and Take a picture at the &ldquo;TOYOTA YARIS&rdquo; contest area, at the mall activity, Upload the picture to your Facebook page with the hashtag #TOYOTAYARISAT(Mall Name) and add the tag @Toyotaindia, during upload on Facebook, the participant must set the Facebook profile permissions as PUBLIC for the image and must retain the public profile status till the overall activity closing date; post completion of the activity on Sunday (DD/MM/YYYY) at 23:59 hours, so the organisers may track the likes received on the post.</li>
            <li>On or before 23:59 hours on (DD/MM/2018), the participant must take a screenshot of the post, clearly showing the number of likes received on the contest post and share it on: <a href="mailto:toyotayariscontest@gmail.com">toyotayariscontest2018@gmail.com</a>, along with their name, contact number and email id, mentioned in the email body copy. The organisers will then cross check the participant&rsquo;s Facebook page to confirm the number of likes on the contest post, in case the contest post is not public or not visible on the participant&rsquo;s timeline, he or she will not be considered for the final winner selection. Any likes received post 7 days of the upload date shall not be considered and the same will be invalid.</li>
            <li>Winners of the contest will be notified by call or email. The organizer shall not be responsible for delayed entries. The organizers have the sole and absolute right to close or extend the contest by any time frame at their discretion.</li>
            <li>One winner will be selected from each of the activation cities. The participant with the most number of likes, will be declared the winner for his city. In case of a tie between two or more contestants from the same participating city, a lucky draw process will be used to select a winner. The process defined for the lucky draw selection will be as per the organiser&rsquo;s discretion.</li>
            <li>In case the organisers are unable to reach a winner on email and phone number provided by the winner, another winner from that city will be selected.</li>
            <li>If more than one entry is received from the same user, only one such entry of the organizers choice shall be eligible for participation.</li>
            <li>Prizes will be hand delivered to each winner at a time and place of the participant&rsquo;s choosing but within the city of activity only. At the time of receiving the prize, each winner must sign a receipt of the prize and provide a valid photo ID proof.</li>
            <li>The organizer&rsquo;s decision with regards to winner shall be final and binding. No communication or objection shall be entertained in the regard.</li>
            <li>Prices received from the contest shall not be transferable and cannot be exchanged for cash or otherwise.</li>
            <li>Names, addresses, telephone numbers, email identities and/or photographs of winners maybe used by the Organizers at their sole discretion for sending out commercial information and/or for other commercial, publicity or promotional purposes. Winners who do not wish to publish such information may clearly indicate so in a communication sent to organisers by recorded delivery.</li>
            <li>The Organiser shall not be responsible for any loss or damage whatsoever that may be suffered, by any person, as a result of his participation in the contest. The organizers shall also not be responsible for any cost, expense or other liability including any injury, loss, damage, or other consequences whatsoever arising from, suffered or incurred by the winner from or in relation to the prizes.</li>
            <li>The contest shall be subject to the laws of India, including tax laws, rules &amp; regulations, as may be applicable to the winners. The winners shall be solely responsible for payment of applicable taxes to the authorities concerned in respect of the prizes as may be required by law prior to delivery of prizes.</li>
            <li>The organizers offer no guarantee or warranty with respect to any of the prizes. The manufactures, service providers &amp; suppliers of the prizes alone shall be liable for any guarantee or warranty, if any.</li>
            <li>All costs &amp; expenses for collecting, redeeming or utilizing the prize/s will be borne by the respective winner and no claim of whatsoever nature will be entertained by the organizers in this regard. Apart from the entitlement to the prize, the winner or his/her legal heirs will have no other rights to claim against the organizers.</li>
            <li>All decisions of the Organizers in relation to the contest shall be final and binding upon participants and winners. No correspondence or objection shall be entertained in this regard. TKM reserves the right to vary, amend and/or alter any terms of this contest including the right to withdraw the Offer, at any time, without any notice.</li>
            <li>Any disputes arising from or in relation to the contest shall be subject matter to exclusive jurisdiction of competent courts of Ramanagar of Karnataka state only.</li>
            <li>Employees of M/s Toyota Kirloskar Motor Private Limited and/or their associate, subsidiary or joint venture companies and their respective immediate family members shall not be eligible to participate in the contest.</li>
            <li>Participation in this contest implies acceptance of all the terms &amp; conditions of the contest. Participation shall not give any right to the participants to make any claim in connection to the contest and/or its process.</li>
        </ol>
